text: Rosalba formosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 2008. It is known from Santa Cruz, in Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Rosalba formosa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 2008
title: Rosalba formosa
